# Wikipedia - logged in user
Here we test the Wikipedia as a logged in user. We measure the 
[login page](https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:UserLogin&returnto=Main+Page), log in the user and measure when we are redirected back to the main page. We wait for 21 seconds and then 
go the [Barack Obama page](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barack_Obama). When the page finished loading, we then waits another 21 seconds and then go to the [President page](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/President_of_the_United_States).
